	"name": "欠钱的朋友",
	"trigger_condition": {"type": "random", "chance": 0.10, "min_day": 2},
	"text": "你的老友欠了一屁股债，逃到你这里来避风头。\n\n'帮帮我——只要几天就好！'他眼巴巴地看着你。",
	"choices": [
	  {"text": "找机会敲闷棍——拖入灵光一现", "outcome": {"consume_card": "MURDER", "evil": 1, "insight_trigger": true}, "requires_card": "MURDER"},
	  {"text": "帮他偿还债务", "outcome": {"gold": -2, "good": 1}},
